Class PropertyModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.json.bind.model.PropertyModel

    public class PropertyModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements SerializerBindingModel, JsonBindingModel, java.lang.Comparable<PropertyModel>
    A model for class property. Property is JavaBean alike meta information field / getter / setter of a property in class.
